602
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:08,119
Shake hands.

603
00:34:09,039 --> 00:34:10,039
Such a smart boy.

604
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:11,800
You have a dog too?

605
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,599
His name is Zhou Junior.

606
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,000
I raised him

607
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:27,320
